Additionally, it honors the founding lord of {{ill|Fukuoka Domain|ja|福岡藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fukuoka Domain|qq=}}, {{ill|Kuroda Yoshitaka|ja|黒田孝高|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuroda Yoshitaka|qq=}} (Kuroda Kanbei), the first feudal lord {{ill|Kuroda Nagamasa|ja|黒田長政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuroda Nagamasa|qq=}} (Black Warrior Daimyōjin), and the {{ill|Kuroda 24 Generals|ja|黒田二十四騎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuroda 24 Generals|qq=}}, a group of notable warriors who served the Kuroda family.

